  <a class="post-link" href="/install/2020/03/25/Mac_Window_change.html">
    <h2 class="post-title">[Mac] 맥 Window와 MacOS 간의 전환 방법</h2>
  </a>
  <div class="post-meta">
    <ul class="post-tags">
          <li>Mac</li>
        
          <li>Window</li>
        
          <li>BootCamp</li>
        
          <li>Window10</li>
